Package: pctax
Type: Package
Title: Professional Comprehensive Microbiome Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Peng Chen
Maintainer: Peng Chen <pengchen2001@zju.edu.cn>
Authors@R:
    person("Peng", "Chen",email ="pengchen2001@zju.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive suite of tools for analyzing microbiome data. 
  It includes functionalities for alpha diversity analysis, beta diversity analysis, differential analysis, 
  community assembly, visualization of phylogenetic tree and functional enrichment analysis... 
  With a progressive approach, the package offers a range of analysis methods to explore and understand the complex microbial communities. 
  It is designed to support researchers and practitioners in conducting in-depth and professional microbiome data analysis.
